cc:Work.dc:title: Double Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: Even though I swore off uploading anymore frames, some of the most viewed files on this account are ironically the cursed frames. So here is another one, a *double frame* .. double the frame, double the pleasure! double frame game! This one was on a clothes ad from a million years ago. The clothes were drab and boring, but the frame, ah the frame, shall live on forever!
